<p>วัสดุที่ใช้ในการทดลองได้แก่ (1) ผังช่วงเวลาดวงจันทร์ (Moon-phase chart) และ (2) ไฟฉายสีแดง (Red flash-light) ใช้สังเกตการณ์ในเวลากลางคืน โดยมีขั้นตอนปฏิบัติ (Procedure) ดังนี้</p><a href="/th/%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%B1%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%A1-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A8%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%A8%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%8C-STEM-%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%8882/">อ่านเนื้อหาทั้งหมด</a> </a> | <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http://taamkru.com/th/%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%B1%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%A1-%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A8%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%A8%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%8C-STEM-%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%8882/" target="_blank">แบ่งปันบน Facebook</a>
